org.eclipse.lyo.client.oslc.resources
Class OslcQuery

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.lyo.client.oslc.resources.OslcQuery

public class OslcQuery
extends Object

Represents an OSLC query (HTTP GET) request to be made of a remote system. Immutable.
